# Task #124: a Sync now that hits the engine's PAIRING_EXPIRED contract (exit 6) must say so
# actionably (not a generic sync error), set the shared flag, and the redrawn menu must carry
# the "! Pairing expired - re-pair" banner at the TOP — picking it opens the re-pair wizard
# (asserted by reaching the wizard's protocol step; the exact-line list check proves the banner
# row really was in the menu).
desc menu (#124): engine rc=6 -> actionable message + flag + top banner -> banner opens re-pair
config paired
seeded
pick 0|Sync now
engine 6|PAIRING_EXPIRED
pick 0|! Pairing expired - re-pair
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace PRES timeout=4 msg='Pairing expired - run Setup / Re-pair'
expect_trace LIST[RomM server protocol]
expect_file .userdata/shared/Lodor/.pairing-expired
